snippet.title: 3D Morpion - Amstrad CPC Gameplay
snippet.description:
3D Morpion is essentially a game akin to 3-D Tic-Tac-Toe, but for the Amstrad CPC. In a four-level cube, try to align four pawns along the diagonals, vertical and horizontal. To do this, simply enter the coordinates of the square to play.

Published as a listing in Hebdogiciel Hors série n° 1 and programmed by Remi Lanne.
